{
 "name": "RPlog_Jedi_Purge_-_Aubrey_s_Death",
 "title": "Jedi Purge: Aubrey's Death",
 "summary": "On the desert training grounds of the Tatooine Jedi School, the corrupted apprentice Cort confronts Aubrey moments after she has slain her friend Priti in a fit of rage. Mocking and goading her, Cort taunts that her fall was her own free will and invites her to join his true master on Dreven. Consumed by grief and hatred, Aubrey attacks, and the two duel up through Cort's torturous training tower, her Dark Side power surging then faltering as the memory of Priti's serene death pulls her back toward the light. At the platform's edge Aubrey renounces her rage and extinguishes her blade in surrender -- and Cort, unmoved, hurls her to her death with a blast of the Force. He claims her lightsaber as a trophy and levitates her broken body back to the school to join those of his other victims.",
